1. Introduction
  a. Purpose: to create a website to play a game online
  b. scope: to have the website userfriendly, well-optimized and supports gaming with the budget
  
2. Requirements
  a. system requirements: need programming softwares, animation features, should have good gpu for renderring
  b. hardware requirements: good hard disks for system, min 16gb ram and graphic cards
  
3. Design
  a. frontend design
  b. backend design
  c. UI- user interface
 
4. Attributes
  a. reliable
  b. user friendly
  c. less ads
  d. should run almost anywhere
  e. product optimized
  f. well updated frequently
